-- installing xtensor
--------------------

Issue with Ubuntu 20.04 xtensor may be missing


http://archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/pool/universe/x/xtensor/xtensor-dev_0.10.11-1_all.deb


sudo dpkg --install xtensor-dev_0.10.11-1_all.deb

